        "## Data Loading\n",
        "\n",
        "I will load the provided CSV files into pandas DataFrames. Based on the file names and the variable names used in the analysis code, I will map them as follows:\n",
        "\n",
        "*   `Rainfall_Ed Dueim.csv` -> `obs_ed_dueim`\n",
        "*   `Rainfall_Kosti.csv` -> `obs_kosti`\n",
        "*   `chirps_Ed Dueim.csv` -> `chirps_ed`\n",
        "*   `chirps_Kosti.csv` -> `chirps_kosti`\n",
        "*   `ERA_5_Ed Dueim.csv` -> `era5_ed`\n",
        "*   `ERA_5 _Kosti.csv` -> `era5_kosti`\n",
        "*   `IMERG_Ed Dueim.csv` -> `imerg_ed`\n",
        "*   `IMERG__Kosti.csv` -> `imerg_kosti`"
      ]
